<div id="review_2590417085" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2590417085" />
    <a title="☘Misericordia☘ ⚡ϟ⚡⛈⚡☁ ❇️❤❣" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6603759-misericordia"><img alt="☘Misericordia☘ ⚡ϟ⚡⛈⚡☁ ❇️❤❣" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1616155242p2/6603759.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2590417085?book_show_action=true">Nov 10, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="☘Misericordia☘ ⚡ϟ⚡⛈⚡☁ ❇️❤❣" class="user" itemprop="url" name="☘Misericordia☘ ⚡ϟ⚡⛈⚡☁ ❇️❤❣" href="/user/show/6603759-misericordia">☘Misericordia☘ ⚡ϟ⚡⛈⚡☁ ❇️❤❣</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2590417085" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14491644230815193067">Q:<br/>He awoke at six, as usual. He needed no alarm clock. He was already comprehensively alarmed. (c)</span>

